description: Imports - Vegetable Plaiting Materials & Veg. Prds. Nie in the United Kingdom increased to 2.53 GBP Million in September from 2.44 GBP Million in August of 2022. Prds in the United Kingdom averaged 2.50 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 111.40 GBP Million in March of 2015 and a record low of 0.56 GBP Million in September of 2000.
